Once upon a time there was a merchant who lived with her daughter in a small village.
one day when he was going to sell his goods.he was passing by the woods.It was a stormy day and his horse coudnt
run anymore. He saw a big palace, so he decided to wait for sometime.He remmemberd that he promised Belle
that on return he will bring rose for her. There was a garden in the palace where he found a rose.But when he took the rose the beast 
got angry and kept him in a jail.The horse saw all this and went back belle and took her to the palace.She told the beast to release her father instead
to keep her in the jail.
